title: (Wed Full)  Having a Fake Wedding to Make Your Ex Jealous + 5 Need to Know Life Hacks + Testing Our Knowledge of George Strait Songs

description:
We talk about a woman who had a fake wedding to get their ex jealous that went viral... does this make her un-dateable? Bobby tells us five life hacks that will make your life easier. Plus, see if we can guess George Strait songs off a one second clip!
